<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 24 日星期三 06:22:27 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Orban: Relations With Sweden 'Awfully Wrong', Preclude It From Joining NATO]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110551691" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/12/1107582042_0:0:2772:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_63c5e8574c39bcbec16d15e2b2c3f618.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1107582024" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/orban-relations-with-sweden-awfully-wrong-preclude-it-from-joining-nato-1110551691.html?share-img=1107582024"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Alexey Vitvitsky</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托在布鲁塞尔欧洲理事会会议期间。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orban during the European Council meeting in Brussels. - Sputnik International, 1920, 24.05.2023" title="匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托在布鲁塞尔举行的欧洲理事会会议上。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/12/1107582042_0:0:2772:1560_1920x0_80_0_0_858e34524413c0d911f176c4e8544d67.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/12/1107582042_0:0:2772:1560_640x0_80_0_0_1b1713f23ca01a8b6a19226eba9cf1b0.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/12/1107582042_0:0:2772:1560_1280x0_80_0_0_e4625d21ca1182b57456a5ec8f961873.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/12/1107582042_0:0:2772:1560_1920x0_80_0_0_858e34524413c0d911f176c4e8544d67.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Alexey Vitvitsky</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊戈尔·库兹涅佐夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_kuznetsov_igor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">多方报道称，面对土耳其和匈牙利的抵制，瑞典政府考虑将加入北约的目标从7月的维尔纽斯峰会推迟到明年4月的华盛顿会议。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">匈牙利总理维克多·欧尔班在卡塔尔经济论坛上表示，匈牙利和瑞典之间的关系很差，必须在北欧国家申请加入北约之前得到改善。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “瑞典和匈牙利之间的政治关系非常错误，我们必须首先改善，”欧尔班说。 “我们不想首先将冲突引入北约。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110551691" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/orban-relations-with-sweden-awfully-wrong-preclude-it-from-joining-nato-1110551691.html?share-block=1110551693" data-title="&amp;quot;The political relationship between Sweden and Hungary is awfully wrong, and we have to improve first,&amp;quot; Orban said. &amp;quot;We would not like to import conflicts into NATO first.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此前，欧尔班的幕僚长表示，匈牙利和瑞典的双边关系已跌至<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230407/sweden-hungary-ties-at-a-low-amid-stockholms-nato-bid-orban-aide-warns-1109229166.html" target="_blank">历史最低点</a>。他还指责瑞典政客“<strong>养成了不断质疑匈牙利民主状况的习惯”，</strong>以及“<strong>侮辱匈牙利选民和国会议员，并通过他们侮辱整个匈牙利</strong>”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">目前还没有确定匈牙利议会何时对瑞典申请加入进行投票的日期，该申请必须得到所有现任成员的批准。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">北约秘书长<a href="https://sputniknews.com/person_Jens_Stoltenberg/" target="_blank" data-auto="true">延斯·斯托尔滕贝格</a>在评论欧尔班的最新声明时重申，他希望瑞典的申请能够获得批准，并建议这样做。除其他外，斯托尔滕贝格将土耳其大选和瑞典新的反恐法列为可能促进北欧国家加入的因素。同时，斯托尔滕贝格表示，即将在立陶宛维尔纽斯举行的北约峰会只是提供了“一种可能性，而非保证”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，瑞典媒体一直流传着政府关于瑞典加入北约的计划可能会被推迟的报道。与 7 月在维尔纽斯获得批准不同，现在正在考虑是否有可能仅在明年 4 月于华盛顿举行的欧盟会议上加入北约。除其他外，这引发了自 1930 年代以来主导瑞典政治的重量级政党社会民主党对缺乏 B 计划的批评。就他们而言，现在处于反对党地位的社会民主党呼吁深化北欧合作，如果北约的加入被推迟。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">尽管如此，领导现任少数政府的自由保守派温和<a href="https://sputniknews.com/organization_Moderate_Party_Sweden/" target="_blank" data-auto="true">党</a>外交部长托比亚斯比尔斯特罗姆证实，<a href="https://sputniknews.com/tag_Stockholm/" target="_blank" data-auto="true">斯德哥尔摩</a>的目标是在维尔纽斯峰会期间加入北约。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">瑞典及其邻国<a href="https://sputniknews.com/geo_Finland/" target="_blank" data-auto="true">芬兰</a>去年要求加入北约，理由是乌克兰冲突后欧洲安全格局发生了变化。虽然芬兰继续<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230519/finland-urged-to-maintain-nuclear-bans-despite-nato-membership-1110455270.html" target="_blank">成为成员国</a>，但瑞典的申办却遭到土耳其和匈牙利的阻挠，布达佩斯对<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230327/budapest-urges-sweden-to-stop-insulting-whole-of-hungary-to-get-nato-bid-accepted-1108813533.html" target="_blank">斯德哥尔摩批评</a>欧尔班的民主和法治记录表示不满，安卡拉指责瑞典窝藏它认为是库尔德恐怖分子和，最近，干预土耳其选举。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 24 May 2023 06:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/orban-relations-with-sweden-awfully-wrong-preclude-it-from-joining-nato-1110551691.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/orban-relations-with-sweden-awfully-wrong-preclude-it-from-joining-nato-1110551691.html<category>世界</category><category>维克托欧尔班</category><category>延斯斯托尔滕贝格</category><category>瑞典</category><category>匈牙利</category><category>维尔纽斯</category><category>北约</category><category>社会民主党</category><category>温和党（瑞典）</category><category>北约扩张</category></item><item><title><![CDATA['Smart' Russian SAMs Strike Ukrainian Warplanes, Drones Using AI]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110552181" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110551669_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_19cc446bdf2b4079e6c8e1172c27b65d.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110551651" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/smart-russian-sams-strike-ukrainian-warplanes-drones-using-ai-1110552181.html?share-img=1110551651"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Mikhail Voskresensky</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯的 S-350 Vityaz 导弹系统。档案照片</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Russia's S-350 Vityaz missile system. File photo - Sputnik International, 1920, 24.05.2023" title="俄罗斯的 S-350 Vityaz 导弹系统。档案照片" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110551669_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_741eb452dd9d4a50b16e15d8e0e877e5.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110551669_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_4b783d9cf693f866fefbf62ef9958172.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110551669_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_0fd9148c61aecb3fe32216c88dde6ee2.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110551669_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_741eb452dd9d4a50b16e15d8e0e877e5.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Mikhail Voskresensky</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Oleg Burunov - Sputnik International" title="奥列格布鲁诺夫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/09/0b/1080424846_0:0:2048:2048_100x100_80_0_0_3d7b461f8a98586fa3fe739930816aea.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">奥列格布鲁诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_burunov_oleg/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:o.burunov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">S-350 Vityaz 于 2019 年在俄罗斯武装部队服役，能够有效摧毁弹道和空气动力目标。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一位消息灵通的消息人士告诉人造卫星网，俄罗斯的 S-350 Vityaz 地对空导弹 (SAM) 系统在没有操作员参与的情况下以全自动模式击落了<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/russias-special-military-operation-in-ukraine-and-how-it-is-progressing-1105665248.html" target="_blank">特别行动区内的</a>乌克兰飞机。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>消息人士称，“勇士号在世界上首次对战斗中的乌克兰空中目标进行了全自动探测、跟踪和摧毁；地对空导弹击落了几架乌克兰战机和无人机。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110552181" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/smart-russian-sams-strike-ukrainian-warplanes-drones-using-ai-1110552181.html?share-block=1110552303" data-title="The source said that “for the first time in the world the Vityaz performed the fully automated detection, tracking and destruction of Ukrainian air targets in combat; the surface-to-air missiles downed several Ukrainian warplanes and unmanned aerial vehicles.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据内部人士称，“自动模式的实施基于这样一个原则，即在新出现的空战情况下，人不会取消 SAM 人工智能元素的决定，即操作员只是没有干预系统的运行，从而确认机器选择的运行算法。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">消息人士解释说，Vityaz 同时在主动和被动雷达模式下工作，这增强了 SAM 的抗干扰能力，以及它检测和分类目标的能力。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> S-350 Vityaz 是一种移动防空系统，于 2019 年在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230413/video-russian-armed-forces-hit-ukrainian-firing-positions-with-thermite-shells-1109459044.html" target="_blank">俄罗斯武装部队</a>服役。SAM 旨在摧毁弹道和空气动力目标，包括战斗机、无人机和巡航导弹。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> S-350 的最大射程可达 120 公里（约 75 英里），它可以在 30 公里（约 18.5 英里）的高度与多达 16 个目标交战。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 24 May 2023 05:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/smart-russian-sams-strike-ukrainian-warplanes-drones-using-ai-1110552181.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/smart-russian-sams-strike-ukrainian-warplanes-drones-using-ai-1110552181.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>特别行动</category><category>防空系统</category><category>战机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Illinois Attorney General Releases Report on Sexual Abuse of Children by Catholic Clergy]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110551334" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/12/1099737881_0:0:3066:2047_1440x900_80_0_1_73ff6e55c12b62a9f5f67dcdf31fe556.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1099737864" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/illinois-attorney-general-releases-report-on-sexual-abuse-of-children-by-catholic-clergy-1110551334.html?share-img=1099737864"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Vladimir Astapkovich</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">梵蒂冈圣彼得大教堂的景色。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="A view of St Peter's Cathedral in Vatican. - Sputnik International, 1920, 24.05.2023" title="梵蒂冈圣彼得大教堂的景色。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/12/1099737881_0:161:3066:1886_1920x0_80_0_0_c5a59176173e18366b8ed09aff34ee47.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/12/1099737881_0:161:3066:1886_640x0_80_0_0_90cb1b4c624a6484d75ea858904b7006.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/12/1099737881_0:161:3066:1886_1280x0_80_0_0_14e7f98aa48469d08b10cd05a574a541.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/12/1099737881_0:161:3066:1886_1920x0_80_0_0_c5a59176173e18366b8ed09aff34ee47.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Vladimir Astapkovich</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：伊利诺伊州总检察长夸梅·拉乌尔发布了一份多年调查报告，记录了该州天主教会领袖和神职人员 70 年来对近 2,000 名儿童的性虐待。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我相信教会在支持弱势群体方面做了重要工作；然而，与任何可能享有盛誉的机构一样，天主教会在背叛公众信任时必须承担责任，”拉乌尔在周二的一份报告中说。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “我希望这份近 700 页的报告能够让天主教神职人员对儿童性虐待的幸存者有所了解，既可以揭示那些侵犯其权力和信任地位的人，也可以揭示教会领导层的个人，这些人涵盖了上那次虐待。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110551334" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/illinois-attorney-general-releases-report-on-sexual-abuse-of-children-by-catholic-clergy-1110551334.html?share-block=1110551336" data-title="&quot;It is my hope that this nearly 700-page report will provide some closure to survivors of child sex abuse by Catholic clerics by shining a light both on those who violated their positions of power and trust, and on the individuals in church leadership who covered up that abuse.&quot; "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">新闻稿称，尽管那些实施虐待的人可能永远不会在法庭上被追究责任，但点名他们的目的是为长期默默承受痛苦的幸存者提供公开的会计和治疗措施。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在总检察长展开调查之前，伊利诺伊州的天主教教区公开承认有 103 名经证实的儿童性虐待者。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>然而，该新闻稿称，该报告披露了 451 名天主教神职人员和宗教兄弟的姓名和详细信息，他们在伊利诺伊州天主教教区虐待了多达 1,997 名儿童。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “幸存者的叙述表明，教会未能支持幸存者，忽视或掩盖虐待报告，以及幸存者在出面报告受到虐待时再次成为教会的受害者，”新闻稿说。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “一再地，教会官员将机构的声誉置于保护儿童之上，经常让施暴者蒙受怀疑——让施暴者有机会再次施虐——甚至通过误导公众来掩盖虐待行为。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110551334" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/illinois-attorney-general-releases-report-on-sexual-abuse-of-children-by-catholic-clergy-1110551334.html?share-block=1110551342" data-title="&quot;Repeatedly, church officials prioritized the reputation of the institution over protecting children, frequently giving abusive priests the benefit of the doubt - giving abusers the chance to abuse again - and even covering up the abuse by misleading the public.&quot; "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">新闻稿补充说，作为这项调查的直接结果，教区改进了与调查儿童性虐待指控和公开披露经证实的儿童性虐待者有关的政策。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>最新版本发布之前，马里兰州总检察长办公室发布了自己的报告，详细说明了 80 年来巴尔的摩大主教管区的权威人士——包括神职人员——所犯下的侵权行为。</p><p> 4 月初的报告包括建议马里兰州立法机关修改虐待案件中潜在民事诉讼的诉讼时效。</p></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 24 May 2023 04:03:38 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/illinois-attorney-general-releases-report-on-sexual-abuse-of-children-by-catholic-clergy-1110551334.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/illinois-attorney-general-releases-report-on-sexual-abuse-of-children-by-catholic-clergy-1110551334.html<category>美洲</category><category>伊利诺伊州</category><category>性虐待</category><category>天主教会</category><category>报告</category></item></channel></rss>